      • isAcceptingDeterminable

        public boolean isAcceptingDeterminable()
        Returns true if the accepting of this run can be determined. For classic finite automata on finite words, we can determine the accepting of a run if the whole word has been consumed. For ω-automata, we can determine the accepting of a run if there is a lasso.
        Returns:
        true if the accepting of this run can be determined
